Lions PR celebrates creative excellence in PR and corporate communications, which successfully builds trust and cultivates relationships with credible third-parties, using mainly earned-media tactics or channels to influence public dialogue and ultimately change perceptions and behaviours in ways that protect and enhance the reputation and business of an organisation or brand with its target audiences. #CannesLions2017: PR Lions shortlistThe Cannes Lions PR shortlist has been released, with SA seeing an entry make it to the final round at Cannes Lions 2017...20 hours ago The Grand Prix went to McCann New York&#x2019;s &#x2018;Fearless Girl&#x2019;, in partnership with State Street Global Advisors&#x2019; #SheMakesADifference. A symbol of women in leadership, Fearless Girl was dropped in a place no one could ignore in the middle of the night and became a global phenomenon within 24 hours. Standing strong on Wall Street in honour of International Women&#x2019;s Day 2017, the statue of a daring young girl serves as a reminder that companies with women in leadership perform better. View the full table of winning work below: PR Lions Winners EntrantTitleClientProductAwardMcCANN NEW YORKFEARLESS GIRLSTATE STREET GLOBAL ADVISORSSHE ETFGrand Prix GOODBY SILVERSTEIN & PARTNERS, San FranciscoCHEETOS MUSEUMCHEETOSCHEETOSGold LionOGILVY & MATHER MUMBAISAVLON HEALTHY HANDS CHALK STICKSITC SAVLONSAVLON HEALTHY HANDS CHALK STICKSGold Lion&Co./NoA, CopenhagenTHE DNA JOURNEYMOMONDOMOMONDO TRAVEL SEARCH ENGINEGold LionLIQUIDMINDS, Copenhagen / SANSIR, TorshavnGOOGLE SHEEP VIEWVISIT FAROE ISLANDS & ATLANTIC AIRWAYSTHE FAROE ISLANDSGold LionCLEMENGER BBDO MELBOURNEMEET GRAHAMTRANSPORT ACCIDENT COMMISSION VICTORIATRANSPORT ACCIDENT COMMISSION VICTORIAGold LionOGILVY NEW YORKTHE REFUGEE NATIONAMNESTY INTERNATIONALAWARNESS AROUND THE REFUGEE CAUSEGold LionFCB CHICAGOTEDDY GUNILLINOIS COUNCIL AGAINST HANDGUN VIOLENCEANTI-GUN VIOLENCE EDUCATION, AWARENESS AND LOBBYING IN ILLINOISGold LionDD